title: Joseph Joseph® Twist 2-in-1 Silicone Whisk
description: Another innovative tool from our friends at Joseph Joseph—this is a flat whisk and balloon whisk in one. Simply twist the base of handle to select flat whisk or balloon whisk. The flat whisk setting makes storage easy, and parts are easy to separate for quick cleaning. Whisk is suitable for nonstick cookware.
